TextBody:
Hello,

Thank you for reaching out to us.
Please check if the MTP Advanced Scanning and Printing is enabled under Global Settings. If not, please activate it, Save and then restart the PC as this feature requires a service restart in order to work.
Let us know if afterward the File traces events appear.

Best regards,
Alin Anca

Thank you.
Subject: Netwrix Support Ticket #442513 - CAP Printing Monitoring Problem

TextBody:
Hello,

Thank you for your reply.
We have a SIEM integration section available in the UI that sends Syslog type logs towards an external configurable service.
For more informations about this, please see the section in the user manual for SIEM integration, I will add it also below:
https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/EndpointProtector_5.9.4/page/Content/EndpointProtector/Admin/Appliance/Overview.htm#siem_integration

As you confirmed that the query for which you raised the current ticket is resolved, I will close this ticket now and ask you if additional queries arise, to please raise a new ticket.

Have a nice day,
Best regards,
